#DOC source=/root/yvon/docs/briefs/lifeos-reference/25--email-inbox-system.md strip=7% toon=3% net=10%
T|25 ·|0|A unified inbox across four em accounts w/ inline draft rp — rv, edit and send w/o leaving Mission Control — plus a one-by-one triage mode and a "reply now" queue of pre-drafted replies.
T|25 ·|1|
T|Purp|0|Manage all em from inside the dashboard and save the owner time. The big change in this bd: an inline rp — the owner can rv the draft reply, edit it, and send right from here, never opening the actual em client. The ag (w/ hy) pre-drafts replies for all emails and only asks for input when unsure.
T|Purp|1|
T|Page|0|Title: Inbox, breadcrumb Vibe w/ AI / Inbox.
T|Page|1|Sub-line: "Your single em surface — read, draft, send. This runs on Mail.app. Local AI reads everything; nothing leaves the machine on the read path."
T|Page|2|Buttons: Draft em, Triage mode.
T|Page|3|An "Inbox Zero protocol · twice daily" indicator, X% done, nx sweep time, and an unread count (e.g. 21).
T|Page|4|Account tabs/filters for the four connected accounts, plus filters (All, Action, Reply, Flagged, Waiting, Archive…) and Sort.
T|Page|5|
T|Mess|0|em rows grouped/triaged, each showing sender, subject, a snippet, the draft status, and quick actions. Examples seen:
T|Mess|1|Maria Solano · Brightwave Studio — "Re: Cinematic site for the new collection — timeline?" w/ Reply now + Draft ready chips.
T|Mess|2|Legal — Hartmann & Vogel — "Revised SaaS retainer agreement" → action: Escalate to hy.
T|Mess|3|Stripe Billing — "Action required — re: your payout account" (flagged).
T|Mess|4|Café Mantra · events — "Re: DJ booking availability — August dates."
T|Mess|5|Each row offers inline Reply now, Open draft, Escalate to hy, Open in Mail.
T|Mess|6|
R|Inli|0|Selecting an em reveals the pre-drafted reply inline; the owner can read, edit, and Send directly, or Send back/regenerate.
R|Inli|1|No need to switch to the external mail client.
R|Inli|2|
T|"Wha|0|A contact intelligence card, e.g. Maria Solano:
T|"Wha|1|Relationship / status (e.g. "Prospect · warm"), value (e.g. ~€5k inquiry).
T|"Wha|2|Contact memory — notes pulled from the memory sy (history, preferences, e.g. "Prefers Spanish for small talk, English for business," "fashion drops," last interactions).
T|"Wha|3|Recent threads / timeline of prior messages.
T|"Wha|4|This is the memory sy surfacing per-contact context to inform the reply.
T|"Wha|5|
T|Tria|0|A focused, full-screen mode that steps through emails one at a time ("em X of Y"), showing the message and its draft w/ large action buttons: Send, Edit, Escalate, Archive, Defer, and Exit triage.
T|Tria|1|Goal: get the inbox to zero quickly.
T|Tria|2|
T|"Rep|0|The sy auto-drafts rp for all emails; unless the ag is unsure, in which case the em goes to a rv section where the ag needs the owner's input on the draft.
T|"Rep|1|In the "reply now" section everything is pre-drafted, so the owner just reviews and sends across all four accounts.
T|"Rep|2|Long-term vision: as trust builds, most emails get sent automatically w/ less and less owner input (same draft→auto-send trajectory as sl/nl).
T|"Rep|3|
T|Inte|Runs on Mail.app locally; local AI reads everything on-device on the read path (privacy note). Four accounts connected. hy handles escalations.